import React from 'react'

const IndexPage = () => {
    const [data, setData] = use
  return (
    <>
    <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder='Student Name'/>
    <input type="number" name="rollno" id="rollno" placeholder='Roll Number' />
    <input type="text" name="dept" id="dept" placeholder='Department' />
    <input type="number" name="noofsem" id="noofsem" placeholder='Number of semesters' />
    <button>Next</button>
    </>
  )
}

export default IndexPage
